Keep the existing Home link, remove Counter/Weather/Auth Required links. Keep the AuthorizeView section at the bottom for login/logout/account management.

### Step 11: Add a `Services` directory to the server project

Create `ShipmentTracker/Services/` directory for the `ShipmentServerService.cs` file.

### Step 12: Seed sample data

Create `ShipmentTracker/Data/SeedData.cs`:
```csharp
using ShipmentTracker.Client.Models;

namespace ShipmentTracker.Data;

public static class SeedData
{
